originalText.text: I have found Dr. Delaney to be an excellent dentist over the course of 10+ years.  He takes a very reasonable yet prudent approach to dental care, provides excellent service. Very attentive and has a great staff.  I have nothing negative to report, only good things to say about Dr. D.

originalText.text: Dr. Delaney is a skilled professional, supportive and a pleasure to interact with. He and his team have helped me to improve and maintain my oral and dental health for over 10 years. I recommend him and his wide range of services Five Stars.

originalText.text: This man who I call the gentle giant is amazing. Never in a million years did I think I would go back to the dentist after the horrific experience I had over 10 years ago. Everyone at this dentist office is so nice and they really care. I had anxiety because the last time I went to the dentist I had a wisdom tooth pulled out that left a abscess and had to get put to sleep cut and drained after wards. It was pure torture. My teeth of course got damaged because of the fear I had to go back to a dentist office. Well not anymore Me Delaney even with my tears was so patient with me and made me feel so comfortable. He did a root canal and made sure I didn't feel a thing. They care they really do... I can't go anywhere else, I'm there for life. The assistant is such a sweetheart as well as Ken the receptionist:)
